      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_6fd19caf-4e64-4a4e-9ce7-9592c9a675d9" class="text-block-content">
    <p>View the filtered gradebook content [1].</p>
<p>Applied filter names display in the <strong>Applied Filters</strong> section [2].</p>
<p>To remove a filter, click the<strong> filter option</strong> drop-down menu [3] and click the <strong>Remove Filter</strong> option [4].</p>
<p>To remove all filters, click the <strong>Clear All Filters </strong>link [5].</p>
<p>To view gradebook settings, click the <strong>Settings</strong> icon [6].</p>
  </div>
